				<td colspan="2"><span>On my server (Sol Ro), I have only seen one for sale in the Bazaar for 34.5k I believe.  I only have about 8k, so I am far from ever buying this.
<br />

<br />
I think the biggest plus of having the DotB is that it is Primary instrument and thus you can keep a weapon in off hand, and actually another weapon on the cursor so that you could melee and do chant damage with proper timing of switching the weapon and the drum.
<br />

<br />
I don't know how rare a drop the DotB are, as according to Allahkahzaam, they drop in Siren's Grotto and Karnor's Castle.  Hopefully, sometime, I can get a group or raid deep enough into either of the places to try and get it to drop, as I don't think I will ever have enough plat to buy something like this.</span></td>
